review_blob:
Backlog. Perfect looking beer. Great package, but wax can be a little annoying. 
A: Nice notes of chocolate and caramel, with a touch of plum.
T: Chocolate, coffee, a lil smokey. 
P: Not as thick and sticky as I like it. Low carbonation, good.
Decent aroma and taste, dried fruits and caramel. Nice brownish colour. But I had few more better beers in this style.
